---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
	title="Privacy Policy | TTRPG Games"
	description="Privacy Policy for TTRPG Games, including information about analytics, submitted information, and external links."
>
	<div class="stack header-offset-shell">
		<section class="hero-card">
			<span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<div class="prose hero-prose">
				<p>
					This Privacy Policy explains what information TTRPG Games may collect and
					how that information is used.
				</p>
				<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
				<p>
					We may collect basic technical information such as server logs, device
					information, browser type, and page requests needed to operate and secure
					the site. If you contact us or submit a game suggestion, we may receive
					the information you choose to provide.
				</p>
				<h2>How Information Is Used</h2>
				<p>
					Information may be used to run the site, improve listings, review
					submissions, respond to messages, and understand how visitors use the
					directory.
				</p>
				<h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
				<p>
					The site uses Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand aggregate usage
					patterns and page performance. This helps with editorial decisions and
					site improvements. We do not use analytics on this site to sell personal
					information.
				</p>
				<h2>Third-Party Sites</h2>
				<p>
					Links on this site may send you to publisher, retailer, or review sites.
					Those sites have their own privacy practices, and we are not responsible
					for them.
				</p>
				<h2>Data Sharing</h2>
				<p>
					We do not sell personal information. Information may be shared with
					service providers only as needed to host, secure, or operate the site.
				</p>
				<h2>Updates</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The current version
					will always be posted on this page.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Base>
